Company Overview of Lombardia Capital Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lombardia Capital Partners, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to state and municipal and government entities and pension and profit sharing plans. It also manages accounts for high net worth individuals, pension funds, public and Taft-Hartley plans, endowments, foundations, corporations, and charitable organizations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe. It typically invests in value stocks of large-cap companies with market capitalization above $5 billion, mid-cap companies with market capitalization be...
Lombardia Capital Partners, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to state and municipal and government entities and pension and profit sharing plans. It also manages accounts for high net worth individuals, pension funds, public and Taft-Hartley plans, endowments, foundations, corporations, and charitable organizations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe. It typically invests in value stocks of large-cap companies with market capitalization above $5 billion, mid-cap companies with market capitalization between $1 billion to $20 billion, and small-cap companies with market capitalization between $100 million to $2 billion. The firm employs a fundamental analysis to make investments. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against the Russell 2000 Value Index, Russell Mid Cap Value Index, Russell 3000 Value Index, and Russell 1000 Value Index. The firm conducts in-house research to make investment decisions. It makes its investments in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. Lombardia Capital Partners, LLC was founded in 1989 and is based in Pasadena, California with an additional office in Chicago, Illinois.
Detailed Description


