Craton Equity Partners LLC

                    Craton Equity Partners provides growth capital to small companies in the clean technology and environmental technology sectors. These companies may include water remediation, waste conversion, 'green' building materials, energy generation from renewable sources and ethanol. Craton seeks companies with total enterprise value less than $50 million.                  





