Lombardia Capital Partners, LLC (LCP) is an employee and minority-owned boutique asset manager specializing in U.S. and non-U.S. value equities. LCP offers investment advisory services to institutional, public, corporate, multi-employer, and not-for-profit clients. LCP manages approximately $1.4 billion* from its offices in Southern California and Chicago, IL. LCP’s suite of domestic small cap products paired with our international strategies provide diverse investment opportunities for current and prospective clients.
*As of December 31, 2016




